item.title: CVE-2022-2093|2024-08-03T00:24:44.260Z -- unknown -- wp%20duplicate%20page
item.description: The WP Duplicate Page WordPress plugin before 1.3 does not sanitize and escape some of its settings, which could allow high privilege users such as admin to perform Cross-Site Scripting attacks even when unfiltered_html is disallowed.
